casebody.data:
Blanche Busch et al., Respondents, v. City of New York, Defendant, and Ammek Realty Associates, Inc., Appellant.

(Republished.)

Judgment unanimously reversed, with costs to the appellant and judgment is directed to be entered in favor of the defendant-appellant dismissing the complaint herein, with costs. (See Golub v. Gity of New York, 201 Mise. 866, affd. 282 App. Div. 666.) Present — Peck, P. J., Dore, Callahan, Breitel and Bergan, JJ.
